data.description: Great opportunity for this newer home on 1/4 acre in Paloma Ranch that offers 4 bedrooms + den & 3.5 baths in 2905 SqFt with a spacious great room layout and split bedrooms. The gourmet kitchen offers an abundance of white cabinetry, granite countertops, designer tile backsplash, stainless appliances including a gas cooktop with exhaust hood and wall ovens, butler's pantry, large walk-in pantry, and island with breakfast bar & pendant lighting. Sliding glass doors open out from the great room and dining area to the covered patio and a large backyard with grass for kids & pets to play on, mountain views, and no backyard neighbors. Side yard has an RV gate and slab with room to park your toys! The master bedroom also has access to the backyard and a custom barn door leading into the spa-like ensuite bath which includes two vanities, oversized shower with rain shower head, freestanding soaking tub, and a huge walk-in closet. Two secondary bedrooms have walk-in closets and share a Jack & Jill bath, and another bedroom has a private bath, perfect for guests! Other features include an oversized laundry room, powder room with pedestal sink, wood-look tile floors throughout (no carpet), stone exterior elevation, and a 3 car tandem garage with epoxy floors and service door to the backyard. Schedule your private showing today!
